adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常班次嘅巴士就無<br />\n但會有特別班次同一d 一日團<br />\n要上網搶<br />\n不過我覺得點燈只係影相靚<br />\n我中意日頭個景多d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最鐘意係冬天天光前個景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nPLAN左20-21 係個度住一晚<br />\n跟住CHECK左18年係21號點燈 <br />\n諗住CHECK OUT 完等埋點燈先走<br />\n搵緊有無巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請問你係咪book左房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBOOK左20晚呀</blockquote><br />\n請問你係點book架 我搵左白金秘書但仲未覆</blockquote><br />\n我都係 完全無覆過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22fb478a28c3e44fc43f5fd7cf6e92afbca68733","tid":388644,"uid":30457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:48:07.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆<br />\n非雪景完全唔吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 去個陣大雪"},{"pid":"b23ce5a32904e3ff802ace65b990308e93d520d7","tid":388644,"uid":51747,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:02:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://farm9.staticflickr.com/8237/8501505723_4146978946.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm9.staticflickr.com%2F8237%2F8501505723_4146978946.jpg&h=f82453ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去左兩年點燈先清，第一年去落雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm9.staticflickr.com/8372/8489339842_16d02b6db2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm9.staticflickr.com%2F8372%2F8489339842_16d02b6db2.jpg&h=73414a95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日出前真係好正"},{"pid":"19f532549e6512bbad07c2975e727db6e12f5275","tid":388644,"uid":65012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:10:53.000Z","msg":"夏天去過金澤 白川鄉 高山 上高地<br />\n直接買巴士套票<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw幾中意高山 靜靜地好舒服"},{"pid":"0648c1e8c093672c8b524fd3a704dedee86a4930","tid":388644,"uid":14539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T21:32:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想BOOK 21號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n21 號就應該無可能啦 <br />\n我都係bk 20晚 第二日睇完走"},{"pid":"31916f25587c4fac67807df6432cf8398e20da3d","tid":388644,"uid":14539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T21:33:59.000Z","msg":"自己都仲未好搞得清楚流程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbk 左住係咪唔洗join 1day tour 都得?"},{"pid":"f0130e5c8e6006e738d349d2ee240930d5f6d9a8","tid":388644,"uid":60187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:27:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/07/025722_31bf009b4461a07e472216279ed37943.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F07%2F025722_31bf009b4461a07e472216279ed37943.jpg&h=4cea0faa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大雪到仆街果時去<br />\n乜柒都睇唔到<br />\n仲比d雪係咁打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我上年去睇點燈<br />\n個幾日無落過雪</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 橙</blockquote><br />\n你幾月去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一月中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後個星期就落大雪"},{"pid":"dbb72dbc4731f691723c0dcc2a0e4eceb5e6a882","tid":388644,"uid":35966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:31:14.000Z","msg":"冬天去較好